title: Studio near Bastyr University
posting_body: ['UPDATED STUDIO HOME', 'Located in a quiet neighborhood.', 'This is not a typical apartment complex but a charming cedar-sided home on a 1/3 acre lot.', 'There’s plenty of privacy, surrounded by mature trees.', 'This house has a country feel with the convenience of being in the city.', 'Studio features a bedroom located away from the common living area, making this more like a one bedroom unit.', 'Washer and dryer in the unit.', 'Off street parking.', 'Pets are welcome.', 'Conveniently located near:', 'Bastyr University', 'UW Bothell', 'St. Edwards Park', 'Walk to Wayne Golf Course Park', 'Golf Courses', 'Kayaking', 'Chateau St. Michelle and Woodinville Wineries', 'Boat Launch and Lake Washington', 'Walking distance to Burke Gilman Trail', 'Easy Access to I-405', 'Near Bothell, Kirkland, Bellevue, Woodinville', 'Terms: First/Last month rent, $500 security dep, $250 non-refundable cleaning fee.', 'Additional $250 collected for utilities along with rent at the 1st of the month.', ' 12-month lease.', 'Renters insurance required.', 'Non-smoking.', 'Pets are accepted on a case by case basis and subject to restriction with additional $300 deposit per pet and additional $20 per month.', 'Background Check, recent pay stub, Personal references (professional and/or previous landlord).', 'NO CREDIT CHECK.', 'All information deemed reliable, tenant to verify.', 'Please reply to this AD to request a showing.', ' Appointments scheduled beginning August 1,2022.', ' Please e-mail with a phone number, along with any information you would like to share.']
